abstract: Japan's economy and industry ministry proposed on Monday the gradual release or evaporation of massive amounts of treated but still radioactive water being stored at the tsunami-wrecked Fukushima nuclear plant.
snippet: Japan's economy and industry ministry proposed on Monday the gradual release or evaporation of massive amounts of treated but still radioactive water being stored at the tsunami-wrecked Fukushima nuclear plant.
lead_paragraph: TOKYO — Japan's economy and industry ministry proposed on Monday the gradual release or evaporation of massive amounts of treated but still radioactive water being stored at the tsunami-wrecked Fukushima nuclear plant.
headline_main: Government Proposes Release of Fukushima Water to Sea or Air
headline_print_headline: Government Proposes Release of Fukushima Water to Sea or Air

abstract: The death was the 20th of a service member during combat operations this year.
snippet: The death was the 20th of a service member during combat operations this year.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — An American service member was killed in Afghanistan on Monday, according to military officials, bringing to 20 the number of troops who have died during combat operations this year.
